<% title "Pediatric Boards" %>
<div class = "sites">
  <h1> <%= yield(:title) %> </h1>

  <p>
  Pediatric anesthesiology certification requires having completed a one-year
  fellowship in pediatric anesthesia or, if you completed residency before July
  2012, meeting <strong>grandfathering criteria:</strong>
  </p>

  <ul style = "text-align: left; font-size: 1.6em; list-style: disc">
    <li> Clinical practice for the last 2 years is primarily devoted to pediatric anesthesiology </li>
    <span> OR </span>
    <li> At least 30% of clinical practice, averaged over the last 5 years, is devoted to pediatric anesthesiology </li>
    <span> AND </span>
    <li> Clinical practice must include neonates and children less than 2 </li>
  </ul>

  <p> In addition, you must pass the pediatric anesthesiology examination. </p>
  <p>
  The ABA has posted the <%= external_link_to "content outline", @peds_exam_content %>
  and <%= external_link_to "sample questions", @peds_exam_questions %>.
  </p>
</div>

